==English==

===Etymology===
From Greek ''[[Αοριστος]] (Aoristos)'' "not done, not completed."

===Noun===
'''aorist'''

# a [[verb]] [[tense]] in some [[language]]s ([[Sanskrit]] and [[Classical Greek]]) that expresses a [[past]] [[action]] but does not indicate if it [[continued]] or [[completed]]

